text: This is the bus stop which is located at the front of Bugis Street. It is also within walking distance to Bugis MRT station, Bugis Junction, Bugis+ and several other landmarks in Bugis area. It is a bus stop with shelter and seats. Bus arrival timing and bus route are clearly stated at the bus stop
Across the street you will find a cheap market and cheap fruits. But, many people.
Best spot to buy Singaporean souvenirs
In middle of Bugis Street, get down and start shopping
